ees-sony-movie-billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk/|archive-date=2015-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年3月6日，證實荷德倫確定參演<ref name=HedlundCast>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Garrett Hedlund Seals Lead In Ang Lee's 'Billy Lynn'|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/garrett-hedlund-billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-ang-lee-tristar-1201386841/|accessdate=2015-04-02|work=deadline.com|date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408045511/http://deadline.com/2015/03/garrett-hedlund-billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-ang-lee-tristar-1201386841/|archive-date=2015-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[博·納普|博·納普]]於2015年3月13日加入劇組<ref name=KnappCast>{{cite news|last1=Lowe|first1=Kinsey|title='Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk' Casts Beau Knapp|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-casts-beau-knapp-1201392270/|accessdate=2015-04-04|work=deadline.com|date=2015-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316185249/http://deadline.com/2015/03/billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-casts-beau-knapp-1201392270/|archive-date=2015-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月1日，[[克莉絲汀·史都華|克莉絲汀·史都華]]加入飾演主角比利的姊姊凱瑟琳<ref name=StewartCast>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|last2=Ge|first2=Linda|title=Kristen Stewart in Talks for Ang Lee's 'Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/kristen-stewart-in-talks-for-ang-lees-billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-exclusive/|accessdate=2015-04-02|work=thewrap|date=2015-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404010142/http://www.thewrap.com/kristen-stewart-in-talks-for-ang-lees-billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-exclusive/|archive-date=2015-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，宣布[[班·普瑞特|班·普瑞特]]將飾演賈許一角<ref name=PlattCast>{{cite news|last1=Gerard|first1=Jeremy|title=Ben Platt Joins Cast Of Ang Lee's 'Billy Flynn's Long Halftime Walk'|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/ang-lee-billy-flynnn-ben-platt-1201403055/|accessdate=2015-04-01|work=deadline.com|date=2015-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504135525/h