>。

=== 評價 ===
《比利·林恩的中場戰事》於紐約影展首映後獲得褒貶不一的評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/10/15/billy-lynn-long-halftime-walk-ang-lee-premiere/92123934/|title='Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk' gets mixed reception at NYC premiere|author=Patrick Ryan|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2016-10-15|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016140157/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/10/15/billy-lynn-long-halftime-walk-ang-lee-premiere/92123934/|archive-date=2016-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/10/15/billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-reviews-reactions-nyff-mixed|title=Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk reviews: First reactions from NYFF are mixed|author=Nick Romano|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-10-15|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018143450/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/10/15/billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk-reviews-reactions-nyff-mixed|archive-date=2016-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據160條評論，持有44%的新鮮度，平均得分5.4／10；該網站共識：「《比利·林恩的中場戰事》有著崇高的目標，但缺乏一個足以強力的劇本來實現它們——而它（指電影）在視覺上的創新往往只產生令人分心的效果。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/billy_lynns_long_halftime_walk |title=Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114165502/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/billy_lynns_long_halftime_walk/ |archive-date=2016-11-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分53（滿分100），評價好壞各半參雜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk|title=Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107221104/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/billy-lynns-long-halftime-walk|archive-date=2016-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大多數影評人稱讚其故事和角色內心的發展，但也批評其高清晰技術使人有些出戲。

該片在中國大陸地區上映後反響與北美截然不同，在大陸影迷權威網站豆瓣上，評分高達8.4/10。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://movie.douban.com/subject/25983044/|title=比利·林恩的中场战事 (豆瓣)|accessdate=2017-08-28|work=movie.douban.com|language=zh-hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829073537/https://movie.douban.com/subject/25983044/|archive-date=2017-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 票房 ===
全球票房仅3093万美元，被美国《综艺报》（''Varierty''）认为是2016年最赔钱的五部电影之一。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=9519|title=全球票房慘綠　李安《比利林恩》淪2016五大最賠電影--上報|accessdate=2017-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829034222/http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=9519|archive-date=2017-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年11月11日，電影在美國的兩間戲院[[有限上映|有限上映]]，在其首映週末獲得12萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/arrival-doctor-strange-almost-christmas-weekend-box-office-1201852814/|title=Veterans Day Weekend Skyrockets At The B.O.: ‘Doctor Strange’ Beating ‘Thor 2’ By 6%; ‘Arrival’ Soars To $24M+ – Sunday AM Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-11-13|accessdate=2016-11-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6m0NUbvel?url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/arrival-doctor-strange-almost-christmas-weekend-box-office-1201852814/|archive-date=2016-11-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一周后該片開始在一千一百七十六間戲院廣泛放映但在首映當天僅獲得35萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/11/19/friday-box-office-doctor-strange-gets-tricked-by-fantastic-beasts-as-billy-lynn-bombs/#7f41de8c6e22|title=Friday Box Office: 'Doctor Strange' Gets Tricked By 'Fantastic Beasts' As 'Billy Lynn' Bombs|author=Scott Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2016-11-19|accessdate=2016-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120152020/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/11/19/friday-box-office-doctor-strange-gets-tricked-by-fantastic-beasts-as-billy-lynn-bombs/#7f41de8c6e22#7f41de8c6e22|archive-date=2016-11-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最终在美国本土仅有173万美元左右票房，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=billylynn.htm|title=Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk (2016) - Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2017-08-28|work=www.boxofficemojo.com|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829034651/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=billylynn.htm|archive-date=2017-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>使得《比利·林恩的中場戰事》被認為是三星影業繼去年的《[[走鋼索的人|走鋼索的人]]》後另一部票房失利的電影。[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]認為，並不是缺乏可用的相關設備而造成票房不佳，而是因為影評人和觀眾對於故事本身並無達成共鳴<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-weekend-box-office-doctor-strange-bleed-for-this-1201856955/|title=‘Fantastic Beasts’ Gobbles Up Teen Girl, Vinny Paz & ‘Billy Lynn’…But Is ‘Potter’ Spinoff Big Enough For A New Franchise?|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-11-19|accessdate=2016-11-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6mAOOMfnH?url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-weekend-box-office-doctor-strange-bleed-for-this-1201856955/|archive-date=2016-11-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

中國大陆方面，首週末獲得1170萬美元，為在國際的九個市場中票房最高的國家，最终累计1.62亿人民币，约合2376万美元，<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=billylynn.htm|title=Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk (2016) - International Box Office Results - Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2017-08-28|work=www.boxofficemojo.com|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829034443/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=billylynn.htm|archive-date=2017-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>占其总票房的77%。

台灣方面，首週三天票房為新台幣3000萬元<ref>{{cite news |author1=盧家豪 |title=3天破3千萬 《比利．林恩》台灣首戰奪冠 |url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1051886 |work=[[自由時報|自由時報]] |date=2016-11-15 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201185029/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1051886 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；最終全台票房為新台幣1.14億元<ref>{{cite web |title=全國電影票房截至2017年三月前資訊 |url=https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/全國電影票房截至三月前資訊_公告日期20170405.pdf |website=[[國家電影中心|國家電影中心]] |date=2017-04-05 |access-date=2019-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602165710/https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A_%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F20170405.pdf |archive-date=2019-06-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

